QuestData.Title: The Mage Tower
QuestData.Description:
Well done $n. In testament to the efforts of all forces fighting here, we have come together to complete the construction of the Mage Tower.
All that remains is for you to inspect our work, and complete the construction.
QuestData.LogDescription: Complete the construction of the Mage Tower.

Objectives.Objective: Complete Construction of the Mage Tower
